## How to use in chat

When asking Cursor to generate or modify code, reference the gold-standard file:

```
Create a new API route for patient referrals.
Follow the pattern in @apps/platform/orchestrator/src/flows/flows.controller.ts
and use validation style from @packages/iskandar-gatekeeper/src/auth.ts.
```

This ensures the AI uses **existing, proven patterns** rather than inventing new conventions.
